official_title: A bill to suspend until the close of December 31,1977, the duty on rubber-modified acrylonitrile-methyl acrylate copolymer.

summary.text: Amends the Tariff Schedules of the United States to suspend through December 31, 1977, the customs duty on rubber-modified acrylonitrite-copolymer methyl acrylate.
